---
---
<section class="services" id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">What We <span class="text-gradient">Create</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        We specialize in two core pillars of digital business: high-end, zero-bloat web architectures, and seamless, automated client communication pipelines.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- Service 1: Headless Web Development -->
      <div class="service-card glass-panel">
        <div class="service-icon web-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">Headless Web Development</h3>
        <p class="service-description">
          We build custom, modern web frontends separate from any legacy backend servers or bloated CMS platforms.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>Blazing Fast:</strong> Load times under 500ms for instant client satisfaction.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>Un-Hackable:</strong> Pre-compiled static assets mean zero database injection risks.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>SEO Mastered:</strong> 100% pre-rendered HTML structure that search engines index immediately.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>No Theme Bloat:</strong> Custom coded designs. No page builders dragging down speeds.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 2: WhatsApp Automation -->
      <div class="service-card glass-panel whatsapp-glow">
        <div class="service-icon wa-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-name">WhatsApp Automation</h3>
        <p class="service-description">
          Convert leads, answer client questions, and close bookings automatically, directly where your clients spend their time.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>24/7 AI Chatbot:</strong> Intelligent custom agents answering common FAQs instantly.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>Lead Qualifying:</strong> Automated intake questions before passing hot leads to humans.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>Workflow Triggering:</strong> Send instant WhatsApp notifications on contact form submissions.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="check-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            <span><strong>CRM Syncing:</strong> Store user contact data, order details, and history seamlessly in spreadsheets or databases.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 120px 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 64px auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .service-card {
    padding: 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .service-card.whatsapp-glow:hover {
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }

  .service-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .web-icon {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.03);
    border-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
  }

  .wa-icon {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.03);
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
  }

  .service-name {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-description {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .service-features li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .check-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 3px;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
  }

  .service-card.whatsapp-glow .check-icon {
    color: var(--accent-whatsapp);
  }

  .service-features strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .service-card {
      padding: 32px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
